description: Buttfuck battles against the one and only Spoinky Boingy! Created by two deities, this little guy is actually 3000 years old and has been through a lot! He's left his home after getting bullied, died a bit here and there, killed an alternate universe version of himself in a fit of rage, and now he's a completely different guy after all his murderous wrath recently split from his body. But his number one hater has come back after all this time...and that's the nefarious Cumlord Shitguzzler.
